data.description: Experience captivating LAKEFRONT living in this UPDATED 4bd/2ba Colonial, offering tranquility & comfort! This turnkey STR is conveniently located near Pocono attractions such as Kalahari, Camelback, & Crossings. Off the foyer is a private room perfect for a bedroom or a home office. The heart of this home lies within its open-concept living space, where an Eat-In Kitchen seamlessly connects w/ the Living Room that has a BRICK FIREPLACE & sliders to deck w/ BREATHTAKING VIEWS of the wooded yard, where a delightful hot tub & glimpses of the lake create a picturesque backdrop for relaxation. The converted garage features a game room for endless entertainment, & a SOOTHING SAUNA. 3bds upstairs & a full bath on each floor. Embrace the serenity of nature in this ultra-private lakeside haven!
